REDUCED FOR QUICK SALE!!!!   Great Fixer upper-Seller will make no repairs.  2 miles from Mount Union College
2 Bedrooms up with half bath.  Main floor kitchen, Dining Room(using as 3rd bedroom presently),  Full Bath & Living Room.  2 car garage and fenced yard. Exta bedroom is also set up in basement.  Lots of potential.
Seller has new hot water tank that is not installed yet but will be leaving. Selling "As Is"  Great Investment
